    <title>日常软件推荐~</title>
    <url>/2025/software-share/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#前言"></a> 前言</h1>
<p>常用的软件推荐，告别 CSDN。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
</br>
<h1 id="开发类软件"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#开发类软件"></a> 开发类软件</h1>
<p>只是我自己用的，大佬勿喷，小弟只会用这些，并且用的没有各位大佬顺手~</p>
<h2 id="visual-studio-code-code-editing-redefined"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#visual-studio-code-code-editing-redefined"></a> Visual Studio Code - Code Editing. Redefined</h2>
<p>官网链接： <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9jb2RlLnZpc3VhbHN0dWRpby5jb20v">https://code.visualstudio.com/<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</br>
<h2 id="pycharm-the-only-python-ide-you-need-jetbrains"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#pycharm-the-only-python-ide-you-need-jetbrains"></a> PyCharm: The only Python IDE you need - JetBrains</h2>
<p>官网链接： <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuamV0YnJhaW5zLmNvbS96aC1jbi9weWNoYXJtLw==">https://www.jetbrains.com/zh-cn/pycharm/<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</br>
<h2 id="datagrip"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#datagrip"></a> DataGrip</h2>
<p>官网链接： <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuamV0YnJhaW5zLmNvbS96aC1jbi9kYXRhZ3JpcC8=">https://www.jetbrains.com/zh-cn/datagrip/<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</br>
<h2 id="notepad3"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#notepad3"></a> NOTEPAD3</h2>
<p>GITHUB仓库：<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3Jpem9uZXNvZnQvTm90ZXBhZDM=">https://github.com/rizonesoft/Notepad3<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
<p>下载地址：<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3Jpem9uZXNvZnQvTm90ZXBhZDMvcmVsZWFzZXM=">https://github.com/rizonesoft/Notepad3/releases<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
<p>为啥不推荐 notepad++ ？因为那傻逼作者是个杂种胎毒！台湾永远是中国的！</p>
<p>注意：这个软件新版 release 安装过程有捆绑软件，请自行拒绝安装！！！</p>
</br>
<h1 id="娱乐"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#娱乐"></a> 娱乐</h1>
<p>影音方面的软件，包括一些设置之类的</p>
<h2 id="potplayer"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#potplayer"></a> potplayer</h2>
<p>官网链接：<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9wb3RwbGF5ZXIuZGF1bS5uZXQv">https://potplayer.daum.net/<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
<p>下载链接：<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly90MS5kYXVtY2RuLm5ldC9wb3RwbGF5ZXIvUG90UGxheWVyL1ZlcnNpb24vTGF0ZXN0L1BvdFBsYXllclNldHVwNjQuZXhl">https://t1.daumcdn.net/potplayer/PotPlayer/Version/Latest/PotPlayerSetup64.exe<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
<p>这是我的 potplayer 配置：<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly93d2lnLmxhbnpvdWUuY29tL2lvUGRpMnpjYndqYw==">蓝奏云下载<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span> 使用直接下载后注册即可。或者可以选择性使用的配置</p>
<p><img data-src="https://s2.loli.net/2025/06/22/8G6HLXhroJASesW.png" alt="image-20250622195449785" /></p>
<p><img data-src="https://s2.loli.net/2025/06/22/k9lTdM5mvYiBceO.png" alt="image-20250622195555324" /></p>
<p><img data-src="https://s2.loli.net/2025/06/22/RrUZTQt5wBN1eXG.png" alt="image-20250622195729294" /></p>
<p><img data-src="https://s2.loli.net/2025/06/22/tLiE8QmIfXPAOM6.png" alt="image-20250622195754033" /></p>
<p><strong>bilibili potplayer 插件</strong></p>
<p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2NoZW4zMTAvQmlsaWJpbGlQb3RQbGF5ZXI=">github page<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
<p>适用于 PotPlayer 的 Bilibili 插件。如果配合<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9ncmVhc3lmb3JrLm9yZy96aC1DTi9zY3JpcHRzLzQ2MTgwMC1iaWxpYmlsaXBvdHBsYXllcg==">油猴脚本<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span>，可以直接在网页打开 PotPlayer 进行播放</p>
<p>用什么 edge 看视频和直播，动不动就抽风。用 potplayer 呀~！</p>
</br>
<h2 id="网易云音乐"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#网易云音乐"></a> 网易云音乐</h2>
<p>这玩意去网易云官网下载就好了</p>
<p>官网链接：<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9tdXNpYy4xNjMuY29tLw==">https://music.163.com/<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
<p>下载网站：<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9tdXNpYy4xNjMuY29tLyMvZG93bmxvYWQ=">https://music.163.com/#/download<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</br>
<h1 id="直播类"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#直播类"></a> 直播类</h1>
<p>直播软件和直播插件~</p>
</br>
<h2 id="open-broadcaster-software-obs"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#open-broadcaster-software-obs"></a> Open Broadcaster Software | OBS</h2>
<p>一款直播推流编码软件，开源且很好用。</p>
<p>官网链接：<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9vYnNwcm9qZWN0LmNvbS8=">https://obsproject.com/<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</br>
<h3 id="obs-插件"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#obs-插件"></a> OBS 插件</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>obs-multi-rtmp (多路推流)</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3NvcmF5dWtpL29icy1tdWx0aS1ydG1w">https://github.com/sorayuki/obs-multi-rtmp<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</br>
<blockquote>
<p>obs-composite-blur (模糊插件，可局部模糊)</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL0Zpbml0ZVNpbmd1bGFyaXR5L29icy1jb21wb3NpdGUtYmx1cg==">https://github.com/FiniteSingularity/obs-composite-blur<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</br>
<blockquote>
<p>obs-auto-subtitle (字幕插件，需要最好是连接大厂的语言模型 API)</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3N1bW1lcnNocmltcC9vYnMtYXV0by1zdWJ0aXRsZQ==">https://github.com/summershrimp/obs-auto-subtitle<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
</br>
<blockquote>
<p>waveform (声音可视化)</p>
</blockquote>
<p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3BoYW5kYXNtL3dhdmVmb3Jt">https://github.com/phandasm/waveform<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p>
]]></content>
